data.title: Excellent organic food and deli
data.text: We love going to Wheatsfiled..they offer excellent food..I love their collection of organic wines and cheeses!!highly recommended!!

data.title: Local Co-oping
data.text: I visit co-ops where ever I go.  This co-op is one of the best that I have visited in a long time.  User friendly, and especially kid friendly.

data.title: Healthy Food Option in Ames, Iowa
data.text: This was a great option for us as we were traveling cross country by car with our dog.  Outdoor patio was a lovely place to eat so that our dog could join us. The hot food bar/deli had a nice variety.  Hubby had the frittata and loved it.  I had a variety of foods, but specifically tried the  dolma, since recommended by some locals.   I also tried one of the soups, which was very good. Everything well labeled for those managing allergies or ethics in their food choices.  Some nice wheat free options (cookie was good!) too, which is always nice.
